---
import '../../styles/global.css';
import ToolList from '../../components/ToolList.jsx';
import SEO from '../../components/SEO.astro';
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';

const schemaData = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "CollectionPage",
  "name": "Best AI Design Tools - Toolaroo",
  "description": "The best AI design tools for branding, UI, graphics, and visual creation.",
  "url": "https://toolaroo.com/category/design"
};

const seoProps = {
  title: "Best AI Design Tools – Toolaroo Directory",
  description: "The best AI design tools for branding, UI, graphics, and visual creation.",
  type: "website",
  schema: schemaData
};
---

<Layout title="Best AI Design Tools" description="AI tools for branding, UI, and graphics" seoProps={seoProps}>
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-32 pb-3 border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        Best AI<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"> Design Tools</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-600">Create stunning visuals, branding, and graphics with AI.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-8 sm:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mb-12 prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          AI design tools help creators and businesses produce high-quality graphics, branding assets, and visual content instantly. Whether you're building logos, enhancing UI design, generating illustrations, or editing images, AI drastically speeds up the design workflow.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          From freelance designers to enterprise teams, AI design automation levels the playing field. Even those without formal design training can now create professional visuals, mockups, and brand materials. These tools integrate seamlessly with popular design platforms and offer customizable templates that adapt to your brand guidelines.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          The design industry is experiencing a transformation as AI handles the repetitive aspects — resizing, color matching, layout optimization — freeing designers to focus on strategy, creativity, and unique brand storytelling.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12 p-6 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl border border-blue-200">
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Create stunning visuals with the best AI design tools.</p>
      </div>

      <ToolList client:load category="design" />

      <div class="mt-16 pt-16 border-t border-slate-200 prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">AI-Powered Design: Creativity Meets Automation</h2>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          AI design tools are democratizing visual creation by removing technical barriers and reducing time-to-delivery for design projects. For startups and SMBs without in-house design teams, AI offers affordable alternatives to expensive agency work. For design professionals, these tools boost productivity and enable scaling of projects.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Key Features of AI Design Tools</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-lg text-slate-700 mb-6">
          <li>Logo and branding design generation</li>
          <li>UI/UX mockup and wireframe creation</li>
          <li>Background removal and image enhancement</li>
          <li>Automatic layout and composition suggestions</li>
          <li>Color palette and typography recommendations</li>
          <li>Asset resizing and format conversion</li>
          <li>Template-based design acceleration</li>
          <li>Brand consistency enforcement across projects</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          The best AI design tools combine ease of use with powerful customization options, making them valuable for both quick design iterations and detailed, brand-specific projects. As AI models improve, the quality of generated designs continues to rival professional work.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
